data.description: Don't miss out on this beautiful home in the heart of Prairie Grove. Close to Battlefield State Park with miles of walking and biking trails. Close to Prairie Grove Schools. Far enough out of town to have a little of that country feel. Large living room with gas fireplace. Separate dinning area that can entertain lots of guests or family. Kitchen is nicely setup with a walk-in pantry. Gas cook stove with granite countertops. Spacious main bedroom with a Jacuzzi tub, his and her sink, walk-in shower, and walk-in closet. Backyard has plenty of room for family game nights or sit around the fire-pit. The house had all new energy efficient lighting installed by Ozarks electric. Two car garage. This is a must see house in a growing community. (Sellers have a assumable mortgage for qualified buyers at 2.75 percent interest)
